{"prompt": "Create an informative blog for a parenting advice platform. The layout should feature a gentle coral.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Parenting Insights</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FF7F50; /* Gentle Coral */\n            --secondary-color: #FFE0D9; /* A lighter shade of coral */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --header-footer-bg: #FDF5F0; /* Off-white with a hint of coral */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #E66B4C; /* Slightly darker coral on hover */\n        }\n\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .blog-post h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post .meta {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #777;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post a.read-more {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .blog-post a.read-more:hover {\n            color: #E66B4C;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .blog-post h2 {\n                font-size: 1.5em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Parenting Insights</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#home\">Home</a>\n            <a href=\"#topics\">Topics</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"main-content\">\n\n        <div class=\"blog-post\">\n            <h2>The Art of Gentle Discipline</h2>\n            <div class=\"meta\">Posted on October 26, 2023 by The Parenting Team</div>\n            <p>Exploring effective and compassionate ways to guide children's behavior without resorting to harsh punishment. Discover strategies that foster understanding and cooperation.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"blog-post\">\n            <h2>Nurturing Early Language Development</h2>\n            <div class=\"meta\">Posted on October 25, 2023 by Dr. Anya Sharma</div>\n            <p>Unlock your child's potential with engaging activities and conversational techniques that boost vocabulary, comprehension, and communication skills from infancy.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"blog-post\">\n            <h2>Navigating the Toddler Years with Patience</h2>\n            <div class=\"meta\">Posted on October 24, 2023 by Mark Johnson</div>\n            <p>The toddler phase is full of wonder and challenges. Learn practical tips for managing tantrums, encouraging independence, and building a strong connection with your little one.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"blog-post\">\n            <h2>Building Resilience in Children</h2>\n            <div class=\"meta\">Posted on October 23, 2023 by The Parenting Team</div>\n            <p>Help your children develop the inner strength to face life's challenges. We discuss how to foster a growth mindset and coping mechanisms for success.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Parenting Insights. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}